{{see|Evolution}}
==English==

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''evolution'''

# {{general}} The [[process]] by which something changes to a different [[form]].
# {{biology}} The change in the [[genetic]] [[composition]] of a species' [[population]] over successive [[generation]]s.
# {{mathematics}} The [[extraction]] of a [[root]] of a [[quantity]].

